<lb n="0410a05" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0410a06" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0410a07" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 168 [No. 152(38), No. 167]</head>
<lb n="0410a08" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead>佛說太子<note n="0410001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">墓＝沐【三】＊</note><note n="0410001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">墓＝沐【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0410001"><lem wit="【大】">墓</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">沐</rdg></app>魄經<note n="0410002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔開元…魄〕九字－【三】</note><note n="0410002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔開元…魄〕九字－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410002" word-count="9"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">開元錄云：沐魄或慕魄</note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0410a09" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0410a10" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator">西晉<note n="0410003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">月氏三藏＝三藏法師【三】</note><note n="0410003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">月氏三藏＝三藏法師【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410003"><lem wit="【大】">月氏三藏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">三藏法師</rdg></app>竺法護譯</byline>
<lb n="0410a11" ed="T"/><div type="jing"><p id="pT03p0410a1101">聞如是：</p><p id="pT03p0410a1104" place="inline">一時，佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園，<note n="0410004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（佛）＋告【三】</note><note n="0410004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（佛）＋告【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410004"><lem wit="【大】">告</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">佛告</rdg></app>
<lb n="0410a12" ed="T"/>諸<note n="0410005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">比丘＝弟子【三】</note><note n="0410005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">比丘＝弟子【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410005"><lem wit="【大】">比丘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">弟子</rdg></app>：</p><p id="pT03p0410a1204" place="inline">「昔者有<note n="0410006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（王）＋【三】</note><note n="0410006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（王）＋【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410006"><lem wit="【大】"><space quantity="0"/></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">王</rdg></app>王名<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" cf1="K11n0210_p0373a04" wit="【CBETA】【麗】" cf2="T03n0167_p0408b09">波</lem><rdg wit="【大】">婆</rdg></app>羅&CB00178;。王有一太子，
<lb n="0410a13" ed="T"/>字名<app type="＊" source="0410001"><lem wit="【大】">墓</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">沐</rdg></app>魄，生有無窮之明，端正<note n="0410007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">妙＝好【三】</note><note n="0410007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">妙＝好【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410007"><lem wit="【大】">妙</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">好</rdg></app>潔，無有
<lb n="0410a14" ed="T"/>雙比。父母奇之，供養瞻視，須其長大，當為立
<lb n="0410a15" ed="T"/>字。然太子結舌不語十有三歲，恬惔質朴，志
<lb n="0410a16" ed="T"/>若死灰，<note n="0410008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">意如＝直若【三】</note><note n="0410008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">意如＝直若【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410008"><lem wit="【大】">意如</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">直若</rdg></app>枯木；目不視色，耳不聽音，狀
<lb n="0410a17" ed="T"/>類瘖&CB00484;聾盲之人。於是父母患而<note n="0410009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">厭＝苦【三】</note><note n="0410009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">厭＝苦【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410009"><lem wit="【大】">厭</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">苦</rdg></app>之。</p><p id="pT03p0410a1716" place="inline">「王
<lb n="0410a18" ed="T"/>語夫人：『當奈之何？此子將為他國所笑。』夫
<lb n="0410a19" ed="T"/>人語王：『當召相師相之，知當語不？』王即召
<lb n="0410a20" ed="T"/>婆羅門師，使相太子。婆羅門言：『此子非是世
<lb n="0410a21" ed="T"/>間人，為是熒惑耳。外為端正，內懷不祥；危
<lb n="0410a22" ed="T"/>國滅宗，將至不久。不可畜養，宜當生埋，誅而
<lb n="0410a23" ed="T"/>殺<note n="0410010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">之＋（今）【三】</note><note n="0410010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之＋（今）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410010"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">之今</rdg></app>。不除此子，則絕國嗣。』王語夫人：『當如
<lb n="0410a24" ed="T"/>之何？今<note n="0410011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔若〕－【三】</note><note n="0410011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔若〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410011"><lem wit="【大】">若</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>不除<note n="0410012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此子＝之以往【三】</note><note n="0410012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">此子＝之以往【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410012"><lem wit="【大】">此子</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">之以往</rdg></app>，恐後無復立<note n="0410013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔太〕－【三】</note><note n="0410013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔太〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410013"><lem wit="【大】">太</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>子。』
<lb n="0410a25" ed="T"/>於是夫人隨王所為。</p><p id="pT03p0410a2509" place="inline">「王即召國中大臣共議
<lb n="0410a26" ed="T"/>之。一臣言：『當遠徙深山無人之處。』一臣言：
<lb n="0410a27" ed="T"/>『當沒深水中。』一臣言：『但當隨師所語，掘作深
<lb n="0410a28" ed="T"/>坑而生埋之。』王即隨是一臣所語，即召外陣
<lb n="0410a29" ed="T"/>兵<note n="0410014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三＝二【三】</note><note n="0410014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三＝二【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410014"><lem wit="【大】">三</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">二</rdg></app>千<note n="0410015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔餘〕－【三】</note><note n="0410015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔餘〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410015"><lem wit="【大】">餘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>人，使掘地作藏。給<note n="0410016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">世＝三十歲【三】</note><note n="0410016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">世＝三十歲【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410016"><lem wit="【大】">世</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">三十歲</rdg></app>資糧，侍以<pb n="0410b" ed="T" id="T03.0168.0410b"/>
<lb n="0410b01" ed="T"/>五僕，太子衣<note n="0410017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">服＝被【三】</note><note n="0410017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">服＝被【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410017"><lem wit="【大】">服</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">被</rdg></app>、瓔珞、<note n="0410018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">珠寶＝寶蓋【三】</note><note n="0410018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">珠寶＝寶蓋【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410018"><lem wit="【大】">珠寶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">寶蓋</rdg></app>盡還太子。於是
<lb n="0410b02" ed="T"/>夫人心<note n="0410019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">欲＝用【三】</note><note n="0410019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">欲＝用【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410019"><lem wit="【大】">欲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">用</rdg></app>傷絕：『我獨無相，生子薄命，<note n="0410020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乃＝反【三】</note><note n="0410020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乃＝反【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410020"><lem wit="【大】">乃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">反</rdg></app>值
<lb n="0410b03" ed="T"/>此殃，事不得止。』涕淚哽咽，不能自勝。</p><p id="pT03p0410b0315" place="inline">「於是復
<lb n="0410b04" ed="T"/>送太子著正殿<note n="0410021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">上＝前【三】＊</note><note n="0410021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">上＝前【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0410021"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">前</rdg></app>，五百夫人見太子端正姝
<lb n="0410b05" ed="T"/>好，無有雙比，皆言：『太子何以不語，而當生埋？』
<lb n="0410b06" ed="T"/>五百婇女見太子端正姝好，皆為太子作禮
<lb n="0410b07" ed="T"/>而<note n="0410022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言＋（太子）【三】</note><note n="0410022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言＋（太子）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410022"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">言太子</rdg></app>：『何以不語，而當生埋？』<note n="0410023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（各）＋各【三】</note><note n="0410023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（各）＋各【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410023"><lem wit="【大】">各</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">各各</rdg></app>為太子作<note n="0410024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">其伎＝唱伎【宋】，倡妓【元】【明】</note><note n="0410024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">其伎＝唱伎【宋】，＝倡妓【元】【明】</note><app n="0410024"><lem wit="【大】">其
<lb n="0410b08" ed="T"/>伎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">唱伎</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">倡妓</rdg></app>樂。太子默然，不觀不聽。</p><p id="pT03p0410b0811" place="inline">「<note n="0410025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">復＝於是直【三】</note><note n="0410025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">復＝於是直【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410025"><lem wit="【大】">復</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">於是直</rdg></app>送太子著外
<lb n="0410b09" ed="T"/>殿<app type="＊" source="0410021"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">前</rdg></app>，五百大臣見太子端正姝好，無有雙比，
<lb n="0410b10" ed="T"/>前白大王：『太子非是不語<note n="0410026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔之〕－【三】</note><note n="0410026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔之〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410026"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>人，且<note n="0410027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">復＝小【三】</note><note n="0410027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">復＝小【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410027"><lem wit="【大】">復</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">小</rdg></app>宿留，
<lb n="0410b11" ed="T"/>語在不久。婆羅門<note n="0410028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言＝師【三】</note><note n="0410028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言＝師【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410028"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">師</rdg></app>，不可審信。』王語大臣：
<lb n="0410b12" ed="T"/>『此是國事，非卿所知。』</p><p id="pT03p0410b1209" place="inline">「作藏<note n="0410029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">已＝以【三】</note><note n="0410029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">已＝以【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410029"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">以</rdg></app>訖，來迎太子。
<lb n="0410b13" ed="T"/>王語其僕：『使太子載<note n="0410030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔我〕－【三】</note><note n="0410030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔我〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410030"><lem wit="【大】">我</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>四望象車，令國中
<lb n="0410b14" ed="T"/>人民就觀，太子<note n="0410031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">當＝儻【三】</note><note n="0410031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">當＝儻【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410031"><lem wit="【大】">當</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">儻</rdg></app>語。<note n="0410032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">若＋（其）【三】</note><note n="0410032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">若＋（其）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410032"><lem wit="【大】">若</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">若其</rdg></app>語者，<note n="0410033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">便＝更【三】</note><note n="0410033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">便＝更【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410033"><lem wit="【大】">便</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">更</rdg></app>載來還。』於
<lb n="0410b15" ed="T"/>是太子<note n="0410034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乘＝昇【三】</note><note n="0410034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">乘＝昇【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410034"><lem wit="【大】">乘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">昇</rdg></app>車尋路。國中耆舊大臣皆宛轉車
<lb n="0410b16" ed="T"/>前而言：『太子！要當一語。若不語者，便以車輾
<lb n="0410b17" ed="T"/>我上過<note n="0410035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔去〕－【三】</note><note n="0410035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔去〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410035"><lem wit="【大】">去</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。』遮蠡虎賁扶避使過。遂<note n="0410036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">侍＝將【三】</note><note n="0410036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">侍＝將【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410036"><lem wit="【大】">侍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">將</rdg></app>太子<note n="0410037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">遂到＝到其【三】</note><note n="0410037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">遂到＝到其【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410037"><lem wit="【大】">
<lb n="0410b18" ed="T"/>遂到</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">到其</rdg></app>藏所。時有數千萬人，皆<note n="0410038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">隨＝送【三】</note><note n="0410038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">隨＝送【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410038"><lem wit="【大】">隨</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">送</rdg></app>太子往到藏
<lb n="0410b19" ed="T"/>所，皆塞藏戶，太子復不得前。遮蠡虎賁麾人
<lb n="0410b20" ed="T"/><note n="0410039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">便＝使【三】</note><note n="0410039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">便＝使【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410039"><lem wit="【大】">便</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">使</rdg></app>&CB00230;。太子<note n="0410040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">適＋（欲）【三】</note><note n="0410040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">適＋（欲）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410040"><lem wit="【大】">適</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">適欲</rdg></app>前，飛鳥走獸復<note n="0410041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔驚〕－【三】</note><note n="0410041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔驚〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410041"><lem wit="【大】">驚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>來<note n="0410042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔前〕－【三】</note><note n="0410042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔前〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410042"><lem wit="【大】">前</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>，遶
<lb n="0410b21" ed="T"/>藏三匝，復塞藏戶，太子復不得前。於是<note n="0410043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔太子〕－【三】</note><note n="0410043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔太子〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410043"><lem wit="【大】">太
<lb n="0410b22" ed="T"/>子</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>舉右手，住而言：『我正<note n="0410044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（欲）＋不【三】</note><note n="0410044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（欲）＋不【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410044"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">欲不</rdg></app>語，而當生埋。我適
<lb n="0410b23" ed="T"/>欲語，恐入地獄。我所以不語者，欲安身避害，
<lb n="0410b24" ed="T"/>濟神離苦，是以不語。而信<note n="0410045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">誑＝狂【三】</note><note n="0410045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">誑＝狂【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410045"><lem wit="【大】">誑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">狂</rdg></app>詐之言，謂我
<lb n="0410b25" ed="T"/>聾盲為實瘖&CB00484;。』</p><p id="pT03p0410b2507" place="inline">「是時人民聞太<note n="0410046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">子＋（已）【三】</note><note n="0410046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">子＋（已）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410046"><lem wit="【大】">子</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">子已</rdg></app>語有絕妙
<lb n="0410b26" ed="T"/>之<note n="0410047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">音＝聲【三】</note><note n="0410047" resp="CBETA" type="mod">音＝聲【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410047"><lem wit="【大】">音</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">聲</rdg></app>，世所希聞，行者為止，坐者為<note n="0410048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔之〕－【三】</note><note n="0410048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔之〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410048"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>起，皆
<lb n="0410b27" ed="T"/>言：『太子神聖乃爾。』皆前叩頭，求恩悔過，原赦
<lb n="0410b28" ed="T"/>我罪。其僕聞之，歡喜踊躍，馳白大王：『太子已
<lb n="0410b29" ed="T"/>語，上徹蒼天，下徹黃泉。飛鳥走獸皆來伏聽<pb n="0410c" ed="T" id="T03.0168.0410c"/>
<lb n="0410c01" ed="T"/>於太子前。』</p><p id="pT03p0410c0105" place="inline">「王聞太子語，歡<note n="0410049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">欣＝喜【三】</note><note n="0410049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">欣＝喜【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410049"><lem wit="【大】">欣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">喜</rdg></app>踊躍，即與夫
<lb n="0410c02" ed="T"/>人<note n="0410050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">駕＝乘【三】</note><note n="0410050" resp="CBETA" type="mod">駕＝乘【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410050"><lem wit="【大】">駕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">乘</rdg></app>四望象車，往迎太子。太子顧<note n="0410051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">視＝見【三】</note><note n="0410051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">視＝見【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410051"><lem wit="【大】">視</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">見</rdg></app>父王，
<lb n="0410c03" ed="T"/>下車避道，四拜而起而言：『勞屈父王遠來見
<lb n="0410c04" ed="T"/>迎。今日父子<note n="0410052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔已〕－【三】</note><note n="0410052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔已〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410052"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>生相棄捐，恩愛已乖，骨肉
<lb n="0410c05" ed="T"/><note n="0410053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝已【明】</note><app n="0410053"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">已</rdg></app>離，其義甚愆，不可聽觀。』王語太子：『<note n="0410054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不可不可＝吾無智慧信任邪師忽致於此吾之愚癡其過深矣【三】</note><note n="0410054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不可不可＝吾無智慧信任邪師忽致於此吾之愚癡其過深矣【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410054"><lem wit="【大】">不可！
<lb n="0410c06" ed="T"/>不可</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">吾無智慧信任邪師忽致於此吾之愚癡其過深矣</rdg></app>！汝為智者，當原不及。共還入國，舉位與
<lb n="0410c07" ed="T"/>汝，我自避退。』太子答言：『<note n="0410055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">我＋（已）【三】</note><note n="0410055" resp="CBETA" type="mod">我＋（已）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410055"><lem wit="【大】">我</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">我已</rdg></app>曾為國王，用行
<lb n="0410c08" ed="T"/>有缺漏故，下入地獄六萬餘歲，蒸&CB00827;剝裂，其
<lb n="0410c09" ed="T"/>痛難忍。當此之時，父母寧能知我地獄苦痛
<lb n="0410c10" ed="T"/>劇不？寧能分取我身上痛不？我厭<note n="0410056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔畏〕－【三】</note><note n="0410056" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔畏〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410056"><lem wit="【大】">畏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>地獄
<lb n="0410c11" ed="T"/>苦，是以結舌不語十有三歲，冀得免瑕，除去
<lb n="0410c12" ed="T"/><note n="0410057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">垢＝污【三】</note><note n="0410057" resp="CBETA" type="mod">垢＝污【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410057"><lem wit="【大】">垢</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">污</rdg></app>穢，出於<note n="0410058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">塵埃＝垢塵【三】</note><note n="0410058" resp="CBETA" type="mod">塵埃＝垢塵【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410058"><lem wit="【大】">塵埃</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">垢塵</rdg></app>之外，不與罪會。除憂去累，
<lb n="0410c13" ed="T"/>念生若寄。不可<note n="0410059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">選軟＝潠濡【宋】</note><app n="0410059"><lem wit="【大】">選軟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">潠濡</rdg></app>，去道日遠。高翔遠逝，
<lb n="0410c14" ed="T"/>自濟於世。世間無常，恍<note n="0410060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惚＝忽【宋】【元】</note><app n="0410060"><lem wit="【大】">惚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">忽</rdg></app>如夢；室家歡<note n="0410061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">娛＝喜【三】</note><note n="0410061" resp="CBETA" type="mod">娛＝喜【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410061"><lem wit="【大】">娛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">喜</rdg></app>，
<lb n="0410c15" ed="T"/>須臾間耳；歡樂暫有，憂苦延長。』</p><p id="pT03p0410c1513" place="inline">「王知太子意
<lb n="0410c16" ed="T"/>堅志固，遂聽學道。於是太子棄國捐王，入
<lb n="0410c17" ed="T"/>山求道，思惟禪定。壽終即生<note n="0410062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">兜術＝第四兜率【三】</note><note n="0410062" resp="CBETA" type="mod">兜術＝第四兜率【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410062"><lem wit="【大】">兜術</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">第四兜率</rdg></app>天上，畢
<lb n="0410c18" ed="T"/>天之壽，下生世間，為迦維羅衛王作太子，自
<lb n="0410c19" ed="T"/>致<note n="0410063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">得＝作【三】</note><note n="0410063" resp="CBETA" type="mod">得＝作【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410063"><lem wit="【大】">得</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">作</rdg></app>佛。」</p><p id="pT03p0410c1904" place="inline">佛告阿難：「<note n="0410064" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">爾＝是【三】</note><note n="0410064" resp="CBETA" type="mod">爾＝是【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410064"><lem wit="【大】">爾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">是</rdg></app>時太子<app type="＊" source="0410001"><lem wit="【大】">墓</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">沐</rdg></app>魄者，我身
<lb n="0410c20" ed="T"/>是也；<note n="0410065" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔是〕－【三】</note><note n="0410065" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔是〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410065"><lem wit="【大】">是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>時父王者，今閱頭檀<note n="0410066" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔是也〕－【三】＊</note><note n="0410066" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔是也〕－【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0410066"><lem wit="【大】">是也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>；是時母
<lb n="0410c21" ed="T"/>者，今摩耶<app type="＊" source="0410066"><lem wit="【大】">是也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>；是時侍我五僕者，<note n="0410067" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（今）＋阿【三】</note><note n="0410067" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（今）＋阿【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410067"><lem wit="【大】">阿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">今阿</rdg></app>若拘
<lb n="0410c22" ed="T"/>&CB00444;等是<note n="0410068" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔也〕－【三】</note><note n="0410068" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔也〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0410068"><lem wit="【大】">也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>；是時婆羅門欲生埋我者，今調達<pb n="0411a" ed="T" id="T03.0168.0411a"/>
<lb n="0411a01" ed="T"/>是也，我與調達，世世有怨。」佛說經<note n="0411001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">訖＝已【三】</note><note n="0411001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">訖＝已【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0411001"><lem wit="【大】">訖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">已</rdg></app>，諸弟
<lb n="0411a02" ed="T"/>子、<note n="0411002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔諸〕－【三】</note><note n="0411002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔諸〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0411002"><lem wit="【大】">諸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>天龍、鬼神、帝王、人民皆大歡喜，為佛作
<lb n="0411a03" ed="T"/>禮。</p>
<lb n="0411a04" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead>佛說太子<app type="＊" source="0410001"><lem wit="【大】">墓</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">沐</rdg></app>魄經</jhead></juan></div>
</body></text></TEI.2>
